{"tid":2310433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［612基金］ 剛出Post 緊急呼籲市民捐款！！！","createTime":"2020-12-03T09:08:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T12:47:20.000Z","uid":22556,"like":31,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"90676ae25d658aa5f52e0769436f8a3a7d20c562","tid":2310433,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T09:08:59.000Z","msg":"【 612 基金財務及工作簡報：2020 年 10 月份】<br />\n   <br />\n＊ 報告全文已上載於 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/612Fund_Report\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F612Fund_Report&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPZ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=7606c179\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/612Fund_Report</a> <br />\n＊ 網上捐款 <a href=\"https://donate.612fund.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdonate.612fund.hk&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPZ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=5707c4d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://donate.612fund.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n報告重點：截至 2020 年 10 月 31 日之工作概況<br />\n<br />\n1）可動用結餘 － 截至 10 月 31 日，基金可動用結餘為 1,765 萬。急需香港市民支持基金的人道支援工作。<br />\n2）總收支情況 － 612 人道支援基金由去年 6 月成立至今，接收捐款共 1 億7,007萬元。截至 10 月 30 日，直接向申請人提供之人道支援總額為 1 億3,022萬元，批出項目資助 966萬元。<br />\n3）直接支援 18,262 人次 －  包括提供法律費用、借出保釋金、還押在囚物資、緊急經濟援助、醫療及情緒支援費用等。<br />\n　<br />\n工作報告詳情及各支援細項之用款情況，歡迎參閱 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/612Fund_Report。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F612Fund_Report%E3%80%82&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPZ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=e1c8ddfd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/612Fund_Report。</a><br />\n感謝大家的支持與關注，基金會繼續謹守崗位，為反送中運動的在囚／還押者、被告、被捕者及傷者提供人道支援。<br />\n<br />\n612 人道支援基金<br />\n2020 年 12 月 3 日<br />\n_<br />\n申請熱線：9845 6641 個人資料，絕對保密<br />\n　<br />\n捐款： <a href=\"https://donate.612fund.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdonate.612fund.hk&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPZ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=5707c4d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://donate.612fund.hk</a><br />\nFB： 612人道支援基金 612 Humanitarian Relief Fund<br />\nIG： <a href=\"http://instagram.com/612fund\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2F612fund&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPZ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=fb7e0c92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">instagram.com/612fund</a><br />\nTG： <a href=\"http://t.me/ReliefFund612_Update\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FReliefFund612_Update&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPZ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=0f497eb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/ReliefFund612_Update</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/368482457185258/posts/698310937535740/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F368482457185258%2Fposts%2F698310937535740%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPZ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=5ea38dbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/368482457185258/posts/698310937535740/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"d8620bc0668ddabf2a3475e7708ce4192631a9c4","tid":2310433,"uid":199689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T09:10:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b8af61637730a8cd6999477fb54dd106f19465a7","tid":2310433,"uid":8204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T09:12:46.000Z","msg":"推!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55246c6d8f15beb16bc558381af9e813af4cb7a4","tid":2310433,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T09:13:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dcb29a53128cad56f310f1bf0a688959eec0035a","tid":2310433,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T09:13:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2104ddb2e6070ec5a6